727638f-a.text:
Northern Boulevard, north side, at 245th Street, showing the Douglaston Inn. It was known as the North Shore Hotel in 1873. Northern Boulevard, here, was then called the Flushing
and North Hempstead Turnpike.
P. L. Sperr  April 12, 1927
